Comment: 0,0:00:01.66,0:00:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,845年 因突然出現的超大型巨人
Comment: 0,0:00:06.87,0:00:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,以及盔甲巨人
Comment: 0,0:00:09.36,0:00:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,所有的日常 隨著城牆的破壞一同破滅
Comment: 0,0:00:14.79,0:00:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,人類放棄瑪利亞之牆
Comment: 0,0:00:18.05,0:00:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,失去了兩成的人口以及三分之一的領土
Comment: 0,0:00:21.72,0:00:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,活動領域退後至羅塞之牆
Comment: 0,0:00:27.14,0:00:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,然後...
Comment: 0,0:00:28.64,0:00:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,850年
Comment: 0,0:00:31.10,0:00:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,人類的反擊...
Comment: 0,0:00:33.43,0:00:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,從現在開始!
Comment: 0,0:00:37.38,0:00:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,目標在眼前 超大型巨人
Comment: 0,0:00:41.07,0:00:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這是個機會
Comment: 0,0:00:42.40,0:00:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,絕對不要放過
Comment: 0,0:00:46.88,0:00:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,唷! 五年沒見了呢
Comment: 0,0:00:50.32,0:00:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,OP
Comment: 0,0:03:00.27,0:03:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這傢伙...
Comment: 0,0:03:01.67,0:03:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,居然以固定砲為目標
Comment: 0,0:03:04.92,0:03:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,看來針對開關門也不是偶然
Comment: 0,0:03:08.71,0:03:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,果然這傢伙有...
Comment: 0,0:03:11.83,0:03:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,智慧
Comment: 0,0:03:18.39,0:03:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,但是這是個機會
Comment: 0,0:03:21.03,0:03:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,能破壞城牆的只有他
Comment: 0,0:03:25.47,0:03:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,只要能夠收拾掉他
Comment: 0,0:03:34.96,0:03:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,太弱了
Comment: 0,0:03:38.52,0:03:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,到手啦!
Comment: 0,0:03:43.80,0:03:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,好... 好熱!
Comment: 0,0:03:52.95,0:03:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,上啊!!
Comment: 0,0:04:00.30,0:04:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,打偏了?
Comment: 0,0:04:07.27,0:04:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不...
Comment: 0,0:04:08.99,0:04:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,超大型巨人消失了
Comment: 0,0:04:13.56,0:04:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連 是你打敗的嗎?
Comment: 0,0:04:16.52,0:04:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不對
Comment: 0,0:04:18.50,0:04:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,跟五年前一樣
Comment: 0,0:04:20.50,0:04:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那傢伙突然出現
Comment: 0,0:04:22.34,0:04:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,又突然消失掉
Comment: 0,0:04:26.94,0:04:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,抱歉
Comment: 0,0:04:27.88,0:04:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我讓他跑了
Comment: 0,0:04:28.97,0:04:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你在抱歉什麼 我們根本無法動彈呢
Comment: 0,0:04:31.89,0:04:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,喂 是說這個的時候嗎?
Comment: 0,0:04:34.52,0:04:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,城牆已經被破壞掉了
Comment: 0,0:04:36.44,0:04:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不快點補起來的話 巨人可又要進來了
Comment: 0,0:04:39.97,0:04:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你們在幹嘛?
Comment: 0,0:04:41.49,0:04:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,超大型巨人出現 即視同作戰
Comment: 0,0:04:45.33,0:04:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,立刻回到本部
Comment: 0,0:04:47.07,0:04:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,有和他接觸過的 記得向本部回報
Comment: 0,0:04:49.86,0:04:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是!
Comment: 0,0:04:50.57,0:04:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,期待先遣部隊的好表現
Comment: 0,0:05:09.40,0:05:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,請將帶走的財物縮小在最小範圍內
Comment: 0,0:05:11.60,0:05:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,冷靜地前往避難
Comment: 0,0:05:17.56,0:05:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這裡被突破的話
Comment: 0,0:05:19.39,0:05:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,五年前的慘劇又將再次上演
Comment: 0,0:05:23.45,0:05:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我們要在這裡阻止巨人們前進
Comment: 0,0:05:28.96,0:05:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,迎擊準備
Comment: 0,0:05:32.86,0:05:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,開砲!
Comment: 0,0:05:40.66,0:05:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,上啊!
Comment: 0,0:05:45.66,0:05:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你們這些訓練兵
Comment: 0,0:05:47.39,0:05:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,也是通過了畢業演習的優秀士兵
Comment: 0,0:05:50.59,0:05:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,期待你們在這次作戰中的表現
Comment: 0,0:05:54.11,0:05:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,沒事的 漢娜
Comment: 0,0:05:56.48,0:05:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我一定會保護妳的
Comment: 0,0:05:58.52,0:05:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,法蘭茲...
Comment: 0,0:06:03.36,0:06:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,沒事吧 阿爾敏
Comment: 0,0:06:06.71,0:06:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,沒事的
Comment: 0,0:06:07.96,0:06:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這毛病很快就會停止
Comment: 0,0:06:10.69,0:06:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,但是 現在情況不太妙
Comment: 0,0:06:12.38,0:06:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,就現況而言 我們沒有將8公尺寬的大洞
Comment: 0,0:06:14.96,0:06:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,馬上填補起來的技術
Comment: 0,0:06:17.51,0:06:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,前門附近的那塊岩石也是 到最後還是無法搬回去
Comment: 0,0:06:23.84,0:06:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,在無法修補大洞的這點上 這座城市將會被遺棄
Comment: 0,0:06:32.07,0:06:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,羅塞之牆被突破
Comment: 0,0:06:34.16,0:06:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,也只是時間上的問題
Comment: 0,0:06:36.47,0:06:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,況且只要他們有心
Comment: 0,0:06:39.74,0:06:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,無論何時都能夠將人類趕盡殺絕
Comment: 0,0:06:42.40,0:06:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,阿爾敏
Comment: 0,0:06:44.15,0:06:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,冷靜點!
Comment: 0,0:06:45.60,0:06:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,現在和當時不同
Comment: 0,0:06:47.33,0:06:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,人類已經不會...
Comment: 0,0:06:48.81,0:06:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,再輸給巨人了!
Comment: 0,0:06:55.28,0:06:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,抱歉...
Comment: 0,0:06:57.40,0:06:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,沒事了
Comment: 0,0:07:14.34,0:07:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,喂 你有在認真下嗎?
Comment: 0,0:07:18.65,0:07:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你看 又是我贏了
Comment: 0,0:07:23.19,0:07:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,明明每個月都跟我下一次
Comment: 0,0:07:27.04,0:07:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你還是沒進步呢
Comment: 0,0:07:29.51,0:07:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,皮克希斯
Comment: 0,0:07:30.86,0:07:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不 不
Comment: 0,0:07:32.13,0:07:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我還不夠格贏巴爾托公爵
Comment: 0,0:07:39.61,0:07:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你不是負責南方司令的最高權力者嗎?
Comment: 0,0:07:47.61,0:07:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,以這種程度的技術跟頭腦 是想要怎樣贏巨人呢?
Comment: 0,0:07:52.18,0:07:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,皮克希斯司令
Comment: 0,0:07:53.95,0:07:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,有傳令
Comment: 0,0:07:55.47,0:07:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你想幹嘛? 無禮的...
Comment: 0,0:07:57.37,0:07:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,托洛斯特區出現了超大型巨人
Comment: 0,0:08:00.45,0:08:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,開關門被破壞了
Comment: 0,0:08:16.32,0:08:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這真是好喝的酒
Comment: 0,0:08:18.92,0:08:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,作為戰場上的朋友 我就虛心收下了
Comment: 0,0:08:24.27,0:08:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,喂
Comment: 0,0:08:25.67,0:08:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,等等 皮克希斯
Comment: 0,0:08:28.87,0:08:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,皮克希斯
Comment: 0,0:08:30.17,0:08:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,給我等等
Comment: 0,0:08:31.91,0:08:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我可不允許你離開這裡
Comment: 0,0:08:35.07,0:08:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,立刻給我召集士兵
Comment: 0,0:08:37.03,0:08:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,保衛我的領地
Comment: 0,0:08:40.19,0:08:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這才是你的職務吧
Comment: 0,0:08:45.46,0:08:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,巴爾托公爵
Comment: 0,0:08:47.06,0:08:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,現在托洛斯特區的士兵們可是拼上性命在戰鬥唷
Comment: 0,0:08:52.05,0:08:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,司令 我去準備馬
Comment: 0,0:08:55.39,0:08:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,然後我想恐怕會有很多人失去性命
Comment: 0,0:08:59.52,0:09:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,而現在我在說話的這一刻也是
Comment: 0,0:09:03.50,0:09:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,反正也是些廉價的生命
Comment: 0,0:09:05.24,0:09:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,捨棄掉就好
Comment: 0,0:09:07.14,0:09:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,況且在棋盤上一直輸給我的你 去了狀況也不會有所改變
Comment: 0,0:09:14.33,0:09:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,請您安心 公爵
Comment: 0,0:09:17.11,0:09:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,在實戰上面對巨人的話
Comment: 0,0:09:19.75,0:09:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,沒有司令親自出手的必要
Comment: 0,0:09:25.41,0:09:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,別說了
Comment: 0,0:09:27.97,0:09:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,巴爾托公爵
Comment: 0,0:09:29.60,0:09:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,就請您一如往常地度過安穩的一天
Comment: 0,0:09:36.97,0:09:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,喂...
Comment: 0,0:09:39.23,0:09:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,皮克希斯
Comment: 0,0:09:40.68,0:09:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,給我回來 皮克希斯
Comment: 0,0:09:43.51,0:09:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,皮克希斯!
Comment: 0,0:09:34.95,0:09:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,CM
Comment: 0,0:09:58.16,0:10:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那麼就照平時訓練一樣分成各班
Comment: 0,0:10:00.84,0:10:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,在駐紮軍團的指揮下
Comment: 0,0:10:03.04,0:10:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,進行補給支援 情報傳遞
Comment: 0,0:10:05.29,0:10:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,以及討伐巨人等任務
Comment: 0,0:10:08.38,0:10:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,前衛部由駐紮軍團負責
Comment: 0,0:10:11.39,0:10:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,中衛部由我們率領的訓練兵團負責
Comment: 0,0:10:14.43,0:10:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,而後衛部則以駐紮軍團的精銳部隊負責
Comment: 0,0:10:18.43,0:10:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,依照報告前衛部已經全滅了
Comment: 0,0:10:23.57,0:10:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,外圍的那群廢物
Comment: 0,0:10:25.18,0:10:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,允許了巨人的進攻
Comment: 0,0:10:27.76,0:10:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,也就是說
Comment: 0,0:10:28.85,0:10:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,現在處於的狀況 就算後門遭盔甲巨人破壞也不足為奇
Comment: 0,0:10:36.56,0:10:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,怎麼會...
Comment: 0,0:10:37.65,0:10:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,騙人的吧
Comment: 0,0:10:39.35,0:10:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,羅塞之牆也被破壞掉的話...
Comment: 0,0:10:41.98,0:10:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,正式聽令
Comment: 0,0:10:44.08,0:10:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,現在是前衛部的迎擊期
Comment: 0,0:10:46.96,0:10:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這次作戰的目的只有一個
Comment: 0,0:10:49.38,0:10:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,在居民避難完成以前死守羅塞之牆
Comment: 0,0:10:54.56,0:10:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,然後 我想你們知道的 陣前逃亡將處以死刑
Comment: 0,0:10:59.77,0:11:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,大家準備好獻上自己的心臟!
Comment: 0,0:11:02.25,0:11:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,解散!
Comment: 0,0:11:03.51,0:11:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是!!
Comment: 0,0:11:10.18,0:11:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,為什麼是今天...
Comment: 0,0:11:12.33,0:11:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,明明我明天就能夠到內地去了
Comment: 0,0:11:17.40,0:11:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,沒事吧?
Comment: 0,0:11:24.38,0:11:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不要... 不要... 不要... 不要...
Comment: 0,0:11:34.45,0:11:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,礙眼!
Comment: 0,0:11:36.18,0:11:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,喂 約翰...
Comment: 0,0:11:37.42,0:11:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你怎麼了?
Comment: 0,0:11:38.40,0:11:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你說我怎麼了?
Comment: 0,0:11:40.11,0:11:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,別給我說得這麼悠哉 你這趕著去投胎的傢伙!
Comment: 0,0:11:43.51,0:11:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你是因為自願進入調查軍團 所以早已有送死的覺悟
Comment: 0,0:11:49.92,0:11:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我可是明天開始就要去內地的啊
Comment: 0,0:11:52.24,0:11:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,冷靜點!
Comment: 0,0:11:53.04,0:11:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,冷靜點等死是嗎!?
Comment: 0,0:11:55.02,0:11:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不對 你給我想起來
Comment: 0,0:11:58.11,0:12:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我們在訓練兵團的這三年
Comment: 0,0:12:02.24,0:12:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這三年我們有好幾次都差點死了
Comment: 0,0:12:05.94,0:12:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,也有真的死掉的人
Comment: 0,0:12:08.09,0:12:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,退出的人跟被趕走的人也是
Comment: 0,0:12:11.41,0:12:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,但是我們活了下來
Comment: 0,0:12:13.50,0:12:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,沒錯吧!
Comment: 0,0:12:14.94,0:12:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,就算是今天我們也能夠活下去!
Comment: 0,0:12:19.35,0:12:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,今天活下去
Comment: 0,0:12:21.44,0:12:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,明天不就能去內地了?
Comment: 0,0:12:28.73,0:12:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,該死的
Comment: 0,0:12:31.81,0:12:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,走啦 達茲
Comment: 0,0:12:33.58,0:12:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不要給我一直哭
Comment: 0,0:12:37.42,0:12:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連
Comment: 0,0:12:39.45,0:12:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,一旦戰鬥陷入混亂
Comment: 0,0:12:41.10,0:12:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你就來我身邊
Comment: 0,0:12:42.45,0:12:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,蛤?
Comment: 0,0:12:43.55,0:12:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我跟妳是不同小組的吧?
Comment: 0,0:12:45.93,0:12:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,在混亂之下 就無法如想像般地順利
Comment: 0,0:12:49.41,0:12:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,由我來保護你
Comment: 0,0:12:50.97,0:12:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你在說什...
Comment: 0,0:12:52.16,0:12:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,阿卡曼訓練兵
Comment: 0,0:12:54.48,0:12:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,特別准許妳隸屬後衛部隊
Comment: 0,0:12:56.56,0:12:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,給我跟上來
Comment: 0,0:12:57.44,0:13:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,等... 以我的程度只會拖累大家
Comment: 0,0:13:01.54,0:13:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我不是在問妳的判斷
Comment: 0,0:13:04.44,0:13:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,如今才避難已經晚了
Comment: 0,0:13:06.29,0:13:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,居民的附近需要更多的精銳保護
Comment: 0,0:13:09.40,0:13:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,可是...
Comment: 0,0:13:10.36,0:13:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,喂!
Comment: 0,0:13:12.13,0:13:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,給我適可而止一點 米卡莎
Comment: 0,0:13:14.36,0:13:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不要連妳都給我亂
Comment: 0,0:13:16.88,0:13:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,現在可是人類滅亡的危機
Comment: 0,0:13:19.17,0:13:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,妳在那邊堅持自己的判斷是怎樣
Comment: 0,0:13:26.28,0:13:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,抱歉
Comment: 0,0:13:27.87,0:13:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我不夠冷靜
Comment: 0,0:13:32.13,0:13:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我只有一個請求
Comment: 0,0:13:37.90,0:13:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,請你不要死
Comment: 0,0:13:47.38,0:13:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我不會死的
Comment: 0,0:13:48.92,0:13:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我怎麼可以...
Comment: 0,0:13:50.81,0:13:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,在這邊就死掉呢
Comment: 0,0:13:55.74,0:13:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,因為我還不了解這個世界的真實姿態
Comment: 0,0:14:03.49,0:14:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,遺留下來的歷史文獻裡並沒有紀錄巨人出現的原因
Comment: 0,0:14:09.00,0:14:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,幾乎是完全不明的
Comment: 0,0:14:11.78,0:14:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,現在已經清楚的巨人生態
Comment: 0,0:14:15.13,0:14:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是來自於調查軍團的最新報告書
Comment: 0,0:14:19.12,0:14:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,無法確認巨人具備像人類般的智慧
Comment: 0,0:14:23.16,0:14:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,因此不曾有過跟我們溝通的例子
Comment: 0,0:14:28.83,0:14:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,巨人身體的構造跟其他生物有著根本上的不同
Comment: 0,0:14:33.92,0:14:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,完全沒有生殖器官
Comment: 0,0:14:35.69,0:14:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,繁殖方式也是不明
Comment: 0,0:14:38.37,0:14:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,但幾乎都是男性的體格
Comment: 0,0:14:41.82,0:14:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,他們的身體具有極高的溫度
Comment: 0,0:14:44.69,0:14:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,而且最難以理解的是
Comment: 0,0:14:46.14,0:14:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,對人類以外的生物完全不感興趣
Comment: 0,0:14:51.10,0:14:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,巨人唯一行動原理就是吃人
Comment: 0,0:14:54.98,0:15:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,但從巨人能在無人類的環境下存活百年以上這點來想
Comment: 0,0:15:01.49,0:15:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,能夠推測出進食這點並非必要
Comment: 0,0:15:06.51,0:15:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,也就是說
Comment: 0,0:15:07.61,0:15:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,目的不在於捕食
Comment: 0,0:15:09.67,0:15:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,而是進行殺戮
Comment: 0,0:15:13.79,0:15:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,然後
Comment: 0,0:15:14.73,0:15:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,將人類逼到如此絕境的最大原因是...
Comment: 0,0:15:18.65,0:15:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,巨人令人驚訝的生命力
Comment: 0,0:15:22.45,0:15:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,以前的人類雖然擁有大砲技術
Comment: 0,0:15:25.88,0:15:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不過光是這樣 還是無法與之抗衡
Comment: 0,0:15:28.88,0:15:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,巨人即使頭被打飛也不會死
Comment: 0,0:15:32.13,0:15:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,雖然個體會有差異
Comment: 0,0:15:34.22,0:15:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,但是失去的頭部會在一到兩分鐘內恢復原狀
Comment: 0,0:15:38.01,0:15:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,怎麼會...
Comment: 0,0:15:39.40,0:15:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,明明光是大隻就很難應付了
Comment: 0,0:15:41.44,0:15:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,教官 那麼巨人是不死之身嗎?
Comment: 0,0:15:45.92,0:15:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,並不是不死之身
Comment: 0,0:15:47.96,0:15:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,打倒巨人的方法只有一個
Comment: 0,0:15:51.15,0:15:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,朝這裡下手
Comment: 0,0:15:53.38,0:15:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,巨人一旦這個部位受到嚴重的損傷
Comment: 0,0:15:56.30,0:15:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,就會因無法再生而死亡
Comment: 0,0:15:59.46,0:16:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,因此為了切下較硬的肉塊
Comment: 0,0:16:01.52,0:16:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,就要使用這兩把刀
Comment: 0,0:16:04.30,0:16:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,只要攻擊能夠擊中巨人的要害
Comment: 0,0:16:07.47,0:16:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,就能夠在不令其再生的情況下即刻死亡
Comment: 0,0:16:19.72,0:16:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我說 阿爾敏
Comment: 0,0:16:21.59,0:16:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你不覺得這是個好機會嗎?
Comment: 0,0:16:25.20,0:16:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,在進入調查軍團之前
Comment: 0,0:16:27.91,0:16:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,如果能在首場戰役有所表現
Comment: 0,0:16:30.11,0:16:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,身為新兵的我們
Comment: 0,0:16:31.86,0:16:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,勢必能夠快速晉升
Comment: 0,0:16:41.08,0:16:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是啊... 沒錯
Comment: 0,0:16:43.96,0:16:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我先告訴你們兩個
Comment: 0,0:16:45.58,0:16:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這次自願加入調查軍團的人可多了
Comment: 0,0:16:49.05,0:16:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,剛才雖然被艾連搶先一步
Comment: 0,0:16:51.63,0:16:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不過這次我可不會輸
Comment: 0,0:16:53.07,0:16:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你說的唷 托瑪斯
Comment: 0,0:16:55.07,0:16:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,來比比看誰可以獵到最多隻巨人吧
Comment: 0,0:16:58.25,0:16:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你可別在數量上作弊喔
Comment: 0,0:16:59.64,0:17:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,第三十四班 推進!
Comment: 0,0:17:01.52,0:17:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,前去支援前衛部隊
Comment: 0,0:17:04.48,0:17:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,好!
Comment: 0,0:17:05.23,0:17:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,走吧!!
Comment: 0,0:17:06.07,0:17:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,喔!!
Comment: 0,0:17:30.25,0:17:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,已經有那麼多巨人...
Comment: 0,0:17:32.32,0:17:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,前衛部隊根本全滅了
Comment: 0,0:17:34.83,0:17:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,在搞三小啊 那些平時作威作福的前輩們
Comment: 0,0:17:38.91,0:17:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,絕對不是我太過樂觀
Comment: 0,0:17:41.76,0:17:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這實在是...
Comment: 0,0:17:44.40,0:17:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是奇行種!
Comment: 0,0:17:46.34,0:17:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,快閃開!!
Comment: 0,0:18:04.72,0:18:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,奇怪...?
Comment: 0,0:18:30.69,0:18:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你在幹什麼!
Comment: 0,0:18:33.09,0:18:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連!
Comment: 0,0:18:33.87,0:18:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,住手 別單獨行動!
Comment: 0,0:18:39.08,0:18:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,給我站住!!
Comment: 0,0:18:41.98,0:18:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你竟敢把托瑪斯...
Comment: 0,0:18:44.27,0:18:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我絕對...
Comment: 0,0:18:45.84,0:18:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,絕對不會讓你逃走!!
Comment: 0,0:18:58.69,0:18:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連!
Comment: 0,0:19:00.20,0:19:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連
Comment: 0,0:19:17.77,0:19:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,住手... 住手啊...
Comment: 0,0:19:27.34,0:19:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,為什麼... 我...
Comment: 0,0:19:30.67,0:19:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,會這樣看著夥伴們被吃掉的景象...
Comment: 0,0:19:41.72,0:19:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,為什麼... 我的身體...
Comment: 0,0:19:45.28,0:19:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,會無法動彈呢...
Comment: 0,0:19:57.38,0:19:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,阿... 阿爾敏...
Comment: 0,0:20:01.15,0:20:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連
Comment: 0,0:20:02.73,0:20:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連
Comment: 0,0:20:04.35,0:20:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連!
Comment: 0,0:20:07.28,0:20:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,怎麼了? 阿爾敏
Comment: 0,0:20:08.78,0:20:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這本書是爺爺偷藏起來的
Comment: 0,0:20:12.13,0:20:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是描寫外面世界的書
Comment: 0,0:20:15.58,0:20:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你說是描寫外面世界的書?
Comment: 0,0:20:18.13,0:20:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那不是違禁品嗎?
Comment: 0,0:20:20.78,0:20:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,小心被憲兵團抓走喔
Comment: 0,0:20:22.24,0:20:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,現在不是說這個的時候
Comment: 0,0:20:25.12,0:20:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,根據這本書上的記載
Comment: 0,0:20:26.39,0:20:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這個世界上大半都被名為「大海」的水所包圍著呢!
Comment: 0,0:20:30.46,0:20:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,而且「大海」全部都是鹽水
Comment: 0,0:20:33.24,0:20:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你是說鹽?
Comment: 0,0:20:34.87,0:20:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你騙肖
Comment: 0,0:20:36.03,0:20:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,鹽不是很貴重嗎?
Comment: 0,0:20:38.27,0:20:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,商人一定馬上就會搶光了
Comment: 0,0:20:40.84,0:20:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,「大海」寬廣到取之不盡用之不竭
Comment: 0,0:20:43.67,0:20:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,怎麼可...
Comment: 0,0:20:45.91,0:20:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不只是鹽堆得像座山
Comment: 0,0:20:48.62,0:20:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,火焰的水
Comment: 0,0:20:50.01,0:20:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,結冰的大地
Comment: 0,0:20:51.35,0:20:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,砂的冰原
Comment: 0,0:20:53.14,0:20:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,外面的世界一定比這牆內寬廣好幾倍
Comment: 0,0:20:58.10,0:20:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,外面的世界...
Comment: 0,0:21:00.55,0:21:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,然後 這雖然還是秘密...
Comment: 0,0:21:04.00,0:21:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我爸爸跟媽媽說這次要去外面的世界
Comment: 0,0:21:09.08,0:21:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,外面的世界啊
Comment: 0,0:21:11.45,0:21:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,欸 艾連
Comment: 0,0:21:13.38,0:21:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,如果哪天我們可以到外面的世界探險就好了
Comment: 0,0:21:37.07,0:21:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連!
Comment: 0,0:21:39.48,0:21:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我怎麼可以..死在這裡...
