Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.66,0:00:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}845年 因突然出現的超大型巨人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.87,0:00:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}以及盔甲巨人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.36,0:00:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}所有的日常 隨著城牆的破壞一同破滅
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.79,0:00:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}人類放棄瑪利亞之牆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.05,0:00:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}失去了兩成的人口以及三分之一的領土
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.72,0:00:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}活動領域退後至羅塞之牆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.14,0:00:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}然後...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.64,0:00:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}850年
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.10,0:00:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}人類的反擊...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.43,0:00:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}從現在開始!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.38,0:00:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}目標在眼前 超大型巨人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.07,0:00:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這是個機會
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.40,0:00:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}絕對不要放過
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.88,0:00:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}唷! 五年沒見了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.27,0:03:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這傢伙...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.67,0:03:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}居然以固定砲為目標
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.92,0:03:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}看來針對開關門也不是偶然
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.71,0:03:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}果然這傢伙有...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.83,0:03:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}智慧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.39,0:03:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}但是這是個機會
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.03,0:03:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}能破壞城牆的只有他
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.47,0:03:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}只要能夠收拾掉他
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.96,0:03:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}太弱了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.52,0:03:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}到手啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.80,0:03:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}好... 好熱!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.95,0:03:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}上啊!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.30,0:04:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}打偏了?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.27,0:04:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.99,0:04:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}超大型巨人消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.56,0:04:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連 是你打敗的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.52,0:04:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不對
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.50,0:04:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}跟五年前一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.50,0:04:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}那傢伙突然出現
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.34,0:04:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}又突然消失掉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.94,0:04:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.88,0:04:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我讓他跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.97,0:04:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你在抱歉什麼 我們根本無法動彈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.89,0:04:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}喂 是說這個的時候嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.52,0:04:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}城牆已經被破壞掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.44,0:04:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不快點補起來的話 巨人可又要進來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.97,0:04:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你們在幹嘛?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.49,0:04:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}超大型巨人出現 即視同作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.33,0:04:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}立刻回到本部
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.07,0:04:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}有和他接觸過的 記得向本部回報
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.86,0:04:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.57,0:04:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}期待先遣部隊的好表現
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.40,0:05:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}請將帶走的財物縮小在最小範圍內
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.60,0:05:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}冷靜地前往避難
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.56,0:05:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這裡被突破的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.39,0:05:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}五年前的慘劇又將再次上演
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.45,0:05:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我們要在這裡阻止巨人們前進
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.96,0:05:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}迎擊準備
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.86,0:05:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}開砲!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.66,0:05:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}上啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.66,0:05:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你們這些訓練兵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.39,0:05:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}也是通過了畢業演習的優秀士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.59,0:05:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}期待你們在這次作戰中的表現
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.11,0:05:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}沒事的 漢娜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.48,0:05:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我一定會保護妳的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.52,0:05:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}法蘭茲...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.36,0:06:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}沒事吧 阿爾敏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.71,0:06:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.96,0:06:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這毛病很快就會停止
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.69,0:06:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}但是 現在情況不太妙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.38,0:06:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就現況而言 我們沒有將8公尺寬的大洞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.96,0:06:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}馬上填補起來的技術
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.51,0:06:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}前門附近的那塊岩石也是 到最後還是無法搬回去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.84,0:06:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}在無法修補大洞的這點上 這座城市將會被遺棄
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.07,0:06:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}羅塞之牆被突破
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.16,0:06:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}也只是時間上的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.47,0:06:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}況且只要他們有心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.74,0:06:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}無論何時都能夠將人類趕盡殺絕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.40,0:06:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}阿爾敏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.15,0:06:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}冷靜點!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.60,0:06:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}現在和當時不同
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.33,0:06:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}人類已經不會...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.81,0:06:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}再輸給巨人了!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.28,0:06:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}抱歉...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.40,0:06:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.34,0:07:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}喂 你有在認真下嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.65,0:07:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你看 又是我贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.19,0:07:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}明明每個月都跟我下一次
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.04,0:07:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你還是沒進步呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.51,0:07:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}皮克希斯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.86,0:07:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不 不
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.13,0:07:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我還不夠格贏巴爾托公爵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.61,0:07:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你不是負責南方司令的最高權力者嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.61,0:07:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}以這種程度的技術跟頭腦 是想要怎樣贏巨人呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.18,0:07:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}皮克希斯司令
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.95,0:07:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}有傳令
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.47,0:07:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你想幹嘛? 無禮的...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.37,0:07:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}托洛斯特區出現了超大型巨人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.45,0:08:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}開關門被破壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.32,0:08:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這真是好喝的酒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.92,0:08:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}作為戰場上的朋友 我就虛心收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.27,0:08:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.67,0:08:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}等等 皮克希斯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.87,0:08:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}皮克希斯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.17,0:08:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}給我等等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.91,0:08:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我可不允許你離開這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.07,0:08:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}立刻給我召集士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.03,0:08:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}保衛我的領地
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.19,0:08:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這才是你的職務吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.46,0:08:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}巴爾托公爵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.06,0:08:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}現在托洛斯特區的士兵們可是拼上性命在戰鬥唷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.05,0:08:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}司令 我去準備馬
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.39,0:08:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}然後我想恐怕會有很多人失去性命
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.52,0:09:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}而現在我在說話的這一刻也是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.50,0:09:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}反正也是些廉價的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.24,0:09:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}捨棄掉就好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.14,0:09:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}況且在棋盤上一直輸給我的你 去了狀況也不會有所改變
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.33,0:09:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}請您安心 公爵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.11,0:09:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}在實戰上面對巨人的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.75,0:09:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}沒有司令親自出手的必要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.41,0:09:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}別說了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.97,0:09:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}巴爾托公爵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.60,0:09:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就請您一如往常地度過安穩的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.97,0:09:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}喂...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.23,0:09:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}皮克希斯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.68,0:09:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}給我回來 皮克希斯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.51,0:09:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}皮克希斯!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.16,0:10:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}那麼就照平時訓練一樣分成各班
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.84,0:10:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}在駐紮軍團的指揮下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.04,0:10:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}進行補給支援 情報傳遞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.29,0:10:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}以及討伐巨人等任務
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.38,0:10:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}前衛部由駐紮軍團負責
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.39,0:10:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}中衛部由我們率領的訓練兵團負責
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.43,0:10:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}而後衛部則以駐紮軍團的精銳部隊負責
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.43,0:10:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}依照報告前衛部已經全滅了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.57,0:10:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}外圍的那群廢物
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.18,0:10:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}允許了巨人的進攻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.76,0:10:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.85,0:10:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}現在處於的狀況 就算後門遭盔甲巨人破壞也不足為奇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.56,0:10:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}怎麼會...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.65,0:10:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}騙人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.35,0:10:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}羅塞之牆也被破壞掉的話...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.98,0:10:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}正式聽令
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.08,0:10:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}現在是前衛部的迎擊期
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.96,0:10:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這次作戰的目的只有一個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.38,0:10:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}在居民避難完成以前死守羅塞之牆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.56,0:10:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}然後 我想你們知道的 陣前逃亡將處以死刑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.77,0:11:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}大家準備好獻上自己的心臟!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.25,0:11:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}解散!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.51,0:11:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.18,0:11:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}為什麼是今天...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.33,0:11:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}明明我明天就能夠到內地去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.40,0:11:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}沒事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.38,0:11:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不要... 不要... 不要... 不要...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.45,0:11:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}礙眼!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.18,0:11:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}喂 約翰...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.42,0:11:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.40,0:11:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你說我怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.11,0:11:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}別給我說得這麼悠哉 你這趕著去投胎的傢伙!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.51,0:11:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你是因為自願進入調查軍團 所以早已有送死的覺悟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.92,0:11:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我可是明天開始就要去內地的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.24,0:11:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}冷靜點!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.04,0:11:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}冷靜點等死是嗎!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.02,0:11:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不對 你給我想起來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.11,0:12:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我們在訓練兵團的這三年
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.24,0:12:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這三年我們有好幾次都差點死了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.94,0:12:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}也有真的死掉的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.09,0:12:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}退出的人跟被趕走的人也是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.41,0:12:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}但是我們活了下來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.50,0:12:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}沒錯吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.94,0:12:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就算是今天我們也能夠活下去!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.35,0:12:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}今天活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.44,0:12:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}明天不就能去內地了?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.73,0:12:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}該死的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.81,0:12:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}走啦 達茲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.58,0:12:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不要給我一直哭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.42,0:12:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.45,0:12:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}一旦戰鬥陷入混亂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.10,0:12:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你就來我身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.45,0:12:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}蛤?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.55,0:12:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我跟妳是不同小組的吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.93,0:12:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}在混亂之下 就無法如想像般地順利
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.41,0:12:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}由我來保護你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.97,0:12:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你在說什...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.16,0:12:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}阿卡曼訓練兵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.48,0:12:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}特別准許妳隸屬後衛部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.56,0:12:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}給我跟上來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.44,0:13:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}等... 以我的程度只會拖累大家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.54,0:13:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我不是在問妳的判斷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.44,0:13:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}如今才避難已經晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.29,0:13:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}居民的附近需要更多的精銳保護
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.40,0:13:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.36,0:13:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}喂!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.13,0:13:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}給我適可而止一點 米卡莎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.36,0:13:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不要連妳都給我亂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.88,0:13:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}現在可是人類滅亡的危機
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.17,0:13:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}妳在那邊堅持自己的判斷是怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.28,0:13:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.87,0:13:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我不夠冷靜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.13,0:13:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我只有一個請求
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.90,0:13:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}請你不要死
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.38,0:13:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我不會死的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.92,0:13:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我怎麼可以...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.81,0:13:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}在這邊就死掉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.74,0:13:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}因為我還不了解這個世界的真實姿態
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.49,0:14:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}遺留下來的歷史文獻裡並沒有紀錄巨人出現的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.00,0:14:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}幾乎是完全不明的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.78,0:14:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}現在已經清楚的巨人生態
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.13,0:14:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是來自於調查軍團的最新報告書
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.12,0:14:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}無法確認巨人具備像人類般的智慧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.16,0:14:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}因此不曾有過跟我們溝通的例子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.83,0:14:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}巨人身體的構造跟其他生物有著根本上的不同
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.92,0:14:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}完全沒有生殖器官
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.69,0:14:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}繁殖方式也是不明
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.37,0:14:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}但幾乎都是男性的體格
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.82,0:14:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}他們的身體具有極高的溫度
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.69,0:14:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}而且最難以理解的是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.14,0:14:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}對人類以外的生物完全不感興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.10,0:14:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}巨人唯一行動原理就是吃人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.98,0:15:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}但從巨人能在無人類的環境下存活百年以上這點來想
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.49,0:15:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}能夠推測出進食這點並非必要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.51,0:15:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.61,0:15:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}目的不在於捕食
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.67,0:15:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}而是進行殺戮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.79,0:15:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}然後
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.73,0:15:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}將人類逼到如此絕境的最大原因是...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.65,0:15:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}巨人令人驚訝的生命力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.45,0:15:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}以前的人類雖然擁有大砲技術
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.88,0:15:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不過光是這樣 還是無法與之抗衡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.88,0:15:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}巨人即使頭被打飛也不會死
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.13,0:15:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}雖然個體會有差異
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.22,0:15:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}但是失去的頭部會在一到兩分鐘內恢復原狀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.01,0:15:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}怎麼會...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.40,0:15:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}明明光是大隻就很難應付了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.44,0:15:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}教官 那麼巨人是不死之身嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.92,0:15:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}並不是不死之身
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.96,0:15:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}打倒巨人的方法只有一個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.15,0:15:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}朝這裡下手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.38,0:15:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}巨人一旦這個部位受到嚴重的損傷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.30,0:15:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就會因無法再生而死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.46,0:16:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}因此為了切下較硬的肉塊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.52,0:16:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就要使用這兩把刀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.30,0:16:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}只要攻擊能夠擊中巨人的要害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.47,0:16:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}就能夠在不令其再生的情況下即刻死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.72,0:16:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我說 阿爾敏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.59,0:16:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你不覺得這是個好機會嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.20,0:16:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}在進入調查軍團之前
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.91,0:16:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}如果能在首場戰役有所表現
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.11,0:16:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}身為新兵的我們
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.86,0:16:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}勢必能夠快速晉升
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.08,0:16:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是啊... 沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.96,0:16:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我先告訴你們兩個
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.58,0:16:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這次自願加入調查軍團的人可多了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.05,0:16:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}剛才雖然被艾連搶先一步
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.63,0:16:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不過這次我可不會輸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.07,0:16:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你說的唷 托瑪斯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.07,0:16:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}來比比看誰可以獵到最多隻巨人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.25,0:16:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你可別在數量上作弊喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.64,0:17:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}第三十四班 推進!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.52,0:17:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}前去支援前衛部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.48,0:17:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}好!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.23,0:17:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}走吧!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.07,0:17:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}喔!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.25,0:17:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}已經有那麼多巨人...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.32,0:17:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}前衛部隊根本全滅了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.83,0:17:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}在搞三小啊 那些平時作威作福的前輩們
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.91,0:17:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}絕對不是我太過樂觀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.76,0:17:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這實在是...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.40,0:17:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是奇行種!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.34,0:17:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}快閃開!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.72,0:18:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}奇怪...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.69,0:18:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你在幹什麼!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.09,0:18:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.87,0:18:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}住手 別單獨行動!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.08,0:18:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}給我站住!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.98,0:18:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你竟敢把托瑪斯...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.27,0:18:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我絕對...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.84,0:18:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}絕對不會讓你逃走!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.69,0:18:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.20,0:19:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.77,0:19:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}住手... 住手啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.34,0:19:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}為什麼... 我...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.67,0:19:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}會這樣看著夥伴們被吃掉的景象...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.72,0:19:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}為什麼... 我的身體...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.28,0:19:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}會無法動彈呢...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.38,0:19:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}阿... 阿爾敏...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.15,0:20:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.73,0:20:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.35,0:20:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.28,0:20:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}怎麼了? 阿爾敏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.78,0:20:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這本書是爺爺偷藏起來的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.13,0:20:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是描寫外面世界的書
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.58,0:20:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你說是描寫外面世界的書?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.13,0:20:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}那不是違禁品嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.78,0:20:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}小心被憲兵團抓走喔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.24,0:20:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}現在不是說這個的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.12,0:20:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}根據這本書上的記載
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.39,0:20:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}這個世界上大半都被名為「大海」的水所包圍著呢!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.46,0:20:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}而且「大海」全部都是鹽水
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.24,0:20:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你是說鹽?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.87,0:20:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}你騙肖
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.03,0:20:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}鹽不是很貴重嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.27,0:20:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}商人一定馬上就會搶光了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.84,0:20:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}「大海」寬廣到取之不盡用之不竭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.67,0:20:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}怎麼可...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.91,0:20:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}不只是鹽堆得像座山
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.62,0:20:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}火焰的水
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.01,0:20:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}結冰的大地
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.35,0:20:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}砂的冰原
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.14,0:20:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}外面的世界一定比這牆內寬廣好幾倍
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.10,0:20:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}外面的世界...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.55,0:21:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}然後 這雖然還是秘密...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.00,0:21:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我爸爸跟媽媽說這次要去外面的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.08,0:21:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}外面的世界啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.45,0:21:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}欸 艾連
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.38,0:21:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}如果哪天我們可以到外面的世界探險就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.07,0:21:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.48,0:21:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我怎麼可以..死在這裡...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.02,0:21:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}阿爾敏
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.53,0:21:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}是你...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.05,0:21:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}告訴我的所以...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.47,0:21:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}我才...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.12,0:21:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}想到外面的...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.86,0:21:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}世界去...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.15,0:22:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}艾連! 快...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.67,0:24:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}突然下起的雨
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.98,0:24:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}那安靜的雨聲
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.07,0:24:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}潮濕的空氣
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.49,0:24:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}微弱的雨之甜味
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.00,0:24:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,fx,{\be5}讓米卡莎想起過去那悽慘的事件
